{"tid":1806041,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［live+得閒update+隨時爛尾］半年東歐exchange","createTime":"2020-01-01T04:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T19:02:45.000Z","uid":171297,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59baf0b55ec9c8364674eb8b52980d71dd40c3a9","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"由於等轉機悶到嘔泡所以又開多個爛尾post<br />\n得閒就記錄下自己嘅exchange生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果㩒入嚟見到呢個post嘅你<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">準備出門未啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n維園見啊！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VgHL5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VgHL5b.jpg&h=70650a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<del><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">代我去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">between富國島遊記會以龜速更新非爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新年快樂及不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b0bbce400c2c65128d842a9f7871b104f566f708","tid":1806041,"uid":69841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADV9aSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADV9aSP.png&h=291c3a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42251cabf34c9e4a60cfb28396a1f9b6ef8c5c9c","tid":1806041,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"去邊個國家"},{"pid":"923d84a9ab4b2bad8f2c4fb9822c65541c97e1dd","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42251cabf34c9e4a60cfb28396a1f9b6ef8c5c9c","tid":1806041,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"去邊個國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"Latvia<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45171021b338576382bbfa9506e1e9e0600585c0","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">Exchange in Latvia / Started at 1/1/2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n揀咗1月1飛仲要凌晨機所以喺機場倒數...<br />\n不過冇人倒數所以我都唔知夠鐘倒數skip埋<br />\n嗌唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光 復 香 港 時 代 革 命 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後指定動作<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZvJvAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZvJvAH.png&h=f016a5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目的地喺Riga 不過冇direct flight所以喺Helsinki轉機<br />\n而我依家就係喺Helsinki等到痴呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次搭Finnair 淨喺搭過兩次長途機嘅我覺得Finnair完勝因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLobExx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLobExx.png&h=fb58dc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGggQFC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGggQFC.png&h=b6bfb461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssqpZy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssqpZy4.png&h=0b6f9bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kem4Zzc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKem4Zzc.png&h=8eefb47d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11個鐘之後終於落機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSWgQGu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSWgQGu.png&h=98221927&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUkQU8g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUkQU8g.png&h=3acff388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知喺咪因為當地時間朝早6點都未夠 過關唔洗排隊 <br />\n不過我喺將兩程飛機分開買 所以要拎行李再check in<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2wgQGK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2wgQGK.png&h=3d0ce6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半個鐘就拎到行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家當地時間朝早7:21 我下一班機喺16:00<br />\n其實有早啲去Riga嘅機 但我預多咗時間比自己以防有咩突發事件...<br />\n所以我等緊下一班早啲開去riga嘅飛機睇下佢可唔可以同情我比我早啲飛走（不過我諗都冇㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n拎住太多行李都唔打算出市區行 遲啲大把機會<br />\n啱啱坐喺T1消滅咗個瑞士卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wa3Cz8X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwa3Cz8X.png&h=aab8a26a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58643cd58ba45996af06f618b1916ac4e3dd5f9d","tid":1806041,"uid":136182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"遲下都去歐洲exchange 留名抄你旅行plan"},{"pid":"106d2fb2a0543806489dedc467c24d7c24b39485","tid":1806041,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0a48b4b69e29b77a4280992ebc31957ea6f6a","tid":1806041,"uid":208829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:54:43.000Z","msg":"lm <br />\n上個sem去exchange 就快完"},{"pid":"d571d0e1711d602670e41e01f5fb9350da8ff9c7","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"［live］Tower Bridge @ London<br />\n<br />\n嚟咗London同朋友會合聽日飛Zurich<br />\n唔知喺咪喺LGW入嘅問題所以勁快過到關連地址都唔洗up<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZobpsMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZobpsMR.png&h=eb772cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家坐喺Tower Bridge橋底等緊我嗰frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話嚟接我結果等咗成嗰鐘都未見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e60c4b70608526cb563eb216638737e575ec51","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T20:59:49.000Z","msg":"13/1/2020 16:30<br />\n同我個frd玩完瑞士 巴塞隆拿同埋巴黎之後<br />\n跟咗佢返倫敦 佢拎行李返香港 我就依家開始獨遊<br />\n嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚我好不安啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知我喺會愛上呢種感覺定喺會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟緊會喺倫敦留多兩日 然後會去愛丁堡留兩日 再喺冰島留四日就返Riga 咩都未plan過 歡迎各位巴絲出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw今日hostel有free dinner<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hxxBnA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hxxBnA.png&h=a2b9b193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然冇肉但有飯食好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d539153703c5693fcbfeaf8376dcca59a17908d6","tid":1806041,"uid":115279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T21:25:21.000Z","msg":"幾年前獨遊過波羅的海三小國，覺得Latvia 係個幾正嘅國家，物價平，景靚，啲人都幾友善，嗰時仲主要係被佢哋抗爭歷史所吸引<br />\n唔知exchange 又係點嘅生活呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e990cbbb55f09429414430f9f24bcea8ff0b6a","tid":1806041,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d539153703c5693fcbfeaf8376dcca59a17908d6","tid":1806041,"uid":11527